<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>MarketHub Forgot Password</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #f4f6f8;
      font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #1c1e21;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 440px;
      margin: 48px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0070f3, #00c6ff);
      padding: 28px 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .header img {
      height: 36px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 40px 32px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.6em;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
      color: #11181c;
    }

    p {
      margin: 0 0 18px 0;
      font-size: 1em;
      color: #4a4f55;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .otp {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 100%;
      letter-spacing: 14px;
      font-size: 2.2em;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: #f0f3f8;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 22px 0;
      color: #0070f3;
      margin: 28px 0 20px 0;
      font-family: 'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, monospace;
    }

    .note {
      font-size: 0.95em;
      color: #6c737f;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 32px 24px 28px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9ea6b0;
      background: #fafbfc;
    }

    @media (max-width: 500px) {
      .container {
        margin: 24px auto;
      }
      .otp {
        letter-spacing: 10px;
        font-size: 2em;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="https://assets.vercel.com/image/upload/front/favicon/vercel/180x180.png" alt="MarketHub Logo">
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Forgot your password?</h2>
      <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>It looks like you requested to reset your MarketHub password. Use the one-time code below to continue:</p>
      <div class="otp"><%= otp %></div>
      <p class="note">
        <strong>Note:</strong> This code will expire in 5 minutes for your security.
      </p>
      <p>If you didnâ€™t request a password change, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> MarketHub. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
